mber 2021}}</ref> |- | 2022–2023 !scope="row"| ''[[Lafuzu]]'' | Jalaal | Recurring role; 2 episodes | style="text-align: center;"|<ref name=Lafuzu/> |- | 2022 !scope="row"| ''[[Office Loabi]]'' | Mohamed Fikury | Main role; 10 episode | style="text-align: center;"| <ref name=OfficeLoabi/> |- | 2022 !scope="row"| ''[[Shakuvaa]]'' | Siraj | Main role; 5 episodes | style="text-align: center;"|<ref name=Lafuzu/> |- | 2022 !scope="row"|''[[Dharaka]]'' | Sameer | Recurring role; 8 episodes | style="text-align: center;" |<ref name=Dharaka/> |- | 2022 !scope="row"|''[[Biruveri Vaahaka]]'' | Rasheed | Main role; Episode: "Lakunu" | style="text-align: center;" |<ref name=BiruveriVaahaka>{{cite news |url=https://www.muniavas.com/40942 |title="Phone Call" - A start to Biruveri Vaahaka |work=MuniAvas |last=Rasheed |first=Ahmed |date=3 June 2022 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220811185353/https://www.muniavas.com/40942 |url-status=live |archivedate=11 August 2022 |access-date=11 August 2022 |df=dmy-all}}</ref> |- | 2022 !scope="row"|''[[Baby (web series)|Baby]]'' | Jaufar | Recurring role; 3 episodes | style="text-align: center;" |<ref name=Baby/> |- | 2022 !scope="row"|''[[Gudhan]]'' | Naseem | Main role; 12 episodes | style="text-align: center;" | <ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.muniavas.com/42756 |title=Fourth episode of "Gudhan" reveals the reason of their trap |language=Divehi |work=MuniAvas |last=Rasheed |first=Ahmed |date=13 September 2022 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20230218052903/https://www.muniavas.com/42756 |url-status= live |archivedate=18 February 2023 |accessdate=18 February 2023 |df=dmy-all}}</ref> |- | 2022 !scope="row"|''[[E Series (web series)|Bahdhal]]'' | Naseem | Recurring role; 3 episodes | style="text-align: center;" |<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.muniavas.com/43259 |title=Fareela's "Badhal" available for streaming through Baiskoafu |language=Divehi |work=MuniAvas |last=Rasheed |first=Ahmed |date=14 October 2022 |archiveurl=https